OL,3,CEaster travel: Millions expected to
OL,4,Ctravel for bank holiday weekend getaway
OL,6,FMotorists in Wales are being urged to
OL,7,Fplan ahead if they're traveling for an
OL,8,Fgetaway. The RAC says avoid peak times
OL,9,Fwith many journeys expected to take
OL,10,Flonger than usual.
OL,12,FThe RAC says 2.6 million cars will
OL,13,Ftake to the roads on Good Friday and
OL,14,Fwarned train passengers to expect
OL,15,Ftrain disruption.
OL,17,FCardiff Queen Street station will be
OL,18,Fclosed between Friday, March 29 and
OL,19,FMonday, April 1 for works on the South
OL,20,FWales Metro transformation.
