OL,3,CEaster travel: Millions expected to
OL,4,Ctravel for bank holiday weekend getaway
OL,6,FEuston Station in London is also shut
OL,7,Fbetween Friday and Easter Monday.
OL,9,FFor those travelling on roads in
OL,10,FWales, the worst times to leave for a
OL,11,Fgetaway are 12.30pm on Good Friday
OL,12,Fwhen the RAC says journeys on the M4
OL,13,Feastbound from to are expected to take
OL,14,F42 minutes - 12 minutes longer than
OL,15,Fusual.
OL,17,FThe worst times to travel back,
OL,18,Fhowever, are Friday, 5 April and
OL,19,FFriday, 12 April, the RAC has said.
