OL,6,FWorst times to return:
OL,8,FRod Dennis, spokesperson for the RAC,
OL,9,Ftold ITV Wales: "Traffic will build in
OL,10,Fthe course of those days.
OL,12,F"The message to drivers is to get away
OL,13,Fas early as you possibly can, or to
OL,14,Fdelay your journey until later into
OL,15,Fthe afternoon if that's an option."
